channel.title: Help? "the command prompt has been disabled by your adminastrator."
channel.description: Well, i wen't to go on my computer after my younger sister had played on it, apparntly she downloaded something that gave me a trojan-backdoor-czp.. I deleted it and qaurrintined it all that, but when i try to run my server or a client it says, "the command prompt has been disabled by your adminastrator", I'm not really sure on what to do, i wen't into my fire-wall and all that but i still can't figure out the problem.. if anyone can help me i would greatly apreciate it.

item.title: Help? "the command prompt has been disabled by your adminastrator."
item.dc:creator: @Ksu Ksu
item.description:
@Ksu wrote:

[quote=“Ksu, post:2, topic:332400”]Click start, run, and enter this:

REG add HKCU\Software\Policies\Microsoft\Windows\System /v DisableCMD /t REG_DWORD /d 0 /f[/quote]
